<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I’m glad I’m not the only one wondering about this! At first I thought I missed something, since Ed went on to confront Hoppo about Mickey at the end <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I’m glad I’m not the only one wondering about this! At first I thought I missed something, since Ed went on to confront Hoppo about Mickey at the end I thought the author was trying to close up loose ends. But I thought at the end the only candidate for the wings on his back was Nicky. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
