      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/52592002-the-chalk-man">Quotes from The Chalk Man</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;What shapes us is not always our achievements but our omissions. Not lies; simply the truths we don’t tell.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/9048805-what-shapes-us-is-not-always-our-achievements-but-our">55 likes</a>
            </nobr>
