          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;There are some things in life you can alter–your weight, your appearance, even your name–but there are others that wishing and trying and working hard can never make any difference to. Those things are the ones that shape us. Not the things we can change, but the ones we can't.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/9069350-there-are-some-things-in-life-you-can-alter-your-weight">48 likes</a>
